description:
ʋɛֆȶǟ is based on 4 Vesta, the largest object in the asteroid belt. the belt is a sprawling place filled with millions of weird celestial bodies, which is represented by the revolving ring.

this is part of my 𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐯𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 collection. it combines my love for space & astronomy, with an abstract monochrome art style. every artwork is a satisfying infinite loop of motion.
